<note n="0444002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444002">〔分邪正品第九〕－【甲】</note>
<note n="0444003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444003">（云）＋何【甲】</note>
<note n="0444004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444004">實亂＝亂實【甲】</note>
<note n="0444005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444005">盡＝悉【甲】</note>
<note n="0444006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444006">（復）＋有【甲】</note>
<note n="0444007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0444007">（般）＋涅【甲】</note>
<note n="0445001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0445001">犯＝判【甲】</note>
<note n="0445002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0445002">此下甲本有觀應元年庚寅十月三日於大和州大御輪寺為西大寺每年講經御本點寫之畢大御輪寺金剛資圓宗俗歲六十五夏次四十五願以點寫力上生都率天願共諸眾生奉見彌勒佛七十一字</note>
</p>
